  ('social-worker-moex-03264', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-114-0e79f916', 'sub-social-worker-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '根據Bowlby所提依附關係的發展階段，若一位幼兒已發展到依附關係的建立，其年齡大約是幾歲？', '["出生至2個月", "3至6個月", "7個月至不足2歲", "2歲以後"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:17+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a087d56213ab", "answer_pdf_sha1": "daeec4fbf76e", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114100", "c": "103", "s": "0305", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "人類行為與社會環境", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、114年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 16, "answer_corrected": true, "flags": ["answer_corrected_skip_v1"], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-03265', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-114-0e79f916', 'sub-social-worker-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '青少年預先設想同學們對其所穿服裝的可能反應後，再依這項預先設想來選擇服裝。此處所預先 設想的同學們，在米德（G.Mead）社會自我論中被稱之為：', '["仿效他人（imitatingother）", "重要他人（significantother）", "概化他人（generalizedother）", "互依他者（interdependentother）"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:17+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a087d56213ab", "answer_pdf_sha1": "daeec4fbf76e", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114100", "c": "103", "s": "0305", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "人類行為與社會環境", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、114年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 17, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
